{"tid":560340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb訛稱遺屬騙財　IT女被捕","createTime":"2018-02-14T04:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T05:46:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a9250dfc8cf0c4894cb61bca48a9b4c3241d4a","tid":560340,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180214/20304978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F20304978&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2B8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e161a79a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F20304978&h=3a7169e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180214/20304978</a><br />\n<br />\nfb訛稱遺屬騙財　IT女被捕<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】大埔公路九巴翻側造成19死65人傷慘劇，全城送暖捐血捐錢之際，卻有冷血女騙徒趁機發死人財，在fb發帖聲稱是死者家屬，指死者遺下一對孖仔，並提供兩個銀行戶口呼籲網民捐款，但被精明網民看穿其騙局報警，警方接報追查後，昨午在旺角拘捕該名女騙徒（圖），並撿走3部手機、一部手提電腦及平板電腦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180214/large/14la3p80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F14la3p80.jpg&h=a5c53689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n指遺下孖仔　網民報警<br />\n<br />\n被捕女子25歲姓張，是一名I.T人，從事網絡設計，涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦被扣查。警方稱相信她單獨犯案，而涉案的兩個銀行戶口相信與疑犯有關，但案中無人有金錢損失。<br />\n<br />\n該個詐騙帖子是於日前在網上社交群組瘋傳，發帖者聲稱「尋好心人」，指在今次大埔翻巴士大車禍中，其姑奶「失去了經濟支柱，遺下一對十個月的孖仔」，又列出兩個銀行戶口號碼，指自己會「暫代收款」，不過有網民即時已質疑有人「發死人財」，除留言提醒網民不要上當，更有超過5名網民報警。警方於大車禍翌日（11日）接獲報案，網絡安全及科技罪案調查科接手調查後，昨午在旺角將騙徒拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎家駒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t政總下半旗致哀　公僕默站<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t家屬偕道士拜祭消防處高層現場默哀<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t「收車」致脫班　車長變磨心<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t今夜馬開賽前默哀1分鐘<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t陳伯：合埋眼就諗起個人頭<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t九巴失控撞欄　車長稱避雀<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t庭上聞19死者名字低頭閉目車長涉危駕還柙　或改控更重罪<br />\n要聞 6小時前"},{"pid":"1a202f5d53576173e877443538d21df56eaf5552","tid":560340,"uid":41821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"又一隻IT9"},{"pid":"f771f24d77634eda886580130f48d090c11465ba","tid":560340,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"明知衰硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bf66837f0512738ccf097a64af451f30aa5249","tid":560340,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"25歲女on99"},{"pid":"d49e82e7b02da0104f79057d80aee1781bf07c50","tid":560340,"uid":166943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"肥婆身形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b121bea48789d01b164a283bf2e7c30c5654628a","tid":560340,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"做IT做到咁撚蠢都有"},{"pid":"ba9b2e6cbb7df3c2294a2623a83c719d9eea6b8e","tid":560340,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9694143790cbcec58a6eb02d01353e1c948349f2","tid":560340,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:15:23.000Z","msg":"肥到..."},{"pid":"d61f17791329e6dbce2b1f416caf80b1d870127b","tid":560340,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"無腦？"},{"pid":"617e97ea9bf20b7f299165d8d3e899e459b4b13b","tid":560340,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ac7be27c463da9edfe3bb467ec0948e3f95916a","tid":560340,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"617e97ea9bf20b7f299165d8d3e899e459b4b13